        <item>
            <title>Xpeng X9 純電 MPV 右軚版抵港，搶先睇車身、內籠設計、詳細規格</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/19/xpeng-x9/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=xpeng-x9</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/19/xpeng-x9/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 07:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[XPENG X9]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1270076</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>XPENG 小鵬汽車推出的全新右軚版本純電 MPV X9 今日正式在香港上市，這新款電動車結合現代化外觀設計、科技功能和舒適的內籠設計，專為追求豪華與科技並存的車主而設，結合商務和家庭用途，亦適合香港用家。</p><p><a title="_DSC2616" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075562519/in/album-72177720321318549" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075562519_21d11bc671_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2616" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2620" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54074358127/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54074358127_69dbc8b24c_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2620" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>XPENG X9 外觀設計延續了小鵬汽車一貫的科技感及豪華感。這款 MPV 的車身尺寸為 5293 x 1988 x 1785 mm，車身高度 1.78 米專為進出香港停車場而設。車身搭載了全球唯一的主動式後輪轉向技術，能夠使轉彎直徑縮小至 10.8 米，轉角最大達到 ±5°，使駕駛更加靈活。配備的智能雙腔空氣懸掛系統，則可以根據車速自動調整車身高度，最多達 90 毫米，以應對不同路況。</p><p><a title="_DSC2624" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075495568/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075495568_d3217fc99d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2624" width="1024" height="611" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC2628" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075495548/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075495548_fb35d15499_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2628" width="1024" height="586" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>X9 內部設計上追求空間感及靈活性，車廂擁有 82 平方尺（7.7 平方米）的寬敞空間，是同級車中最大的車型之一。車內配備了 1,100 毫米的超長電動滑軌和 180 毫米的中央通道，使乘客能輕鬆移動。而第三排座椅則可一鍵電動收納，騰出一個 1.8 米 x 1.6 米的大平台，進一步增強了車內的靈活性和空間利用率。此外行李箱採用下沉式設計，最大容量可達 2,554 公升，足夠放置四個標準高爾夫球袋，極大提升了實用性。</p><p><a title="_DSC2630" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238296/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238296_446a99d656_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2630" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2632" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238266/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238266_7eb2d54e9c_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2632" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2640" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075689230/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075689230_54144629ef_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2640" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2651" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075562469/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075562469_548241d8e6_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2651" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2654" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238276/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238276_2c85bcb1e1_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2654" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2658" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238231/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238231_60fc4c904a_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2658" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2665" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075562494/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075562494_a08710d7fd_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2665" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2666" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238221/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238221_e2fcb701b7_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2666" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>X9 中控台設計簡潔，搭載了 21.4 吋的超大顯示屏幕，為駕駛者提供全面的信息顯示，讓駕駛體驗更加直觀。同時，車內還設有升級選配的零重力座椅，使長途駕駛更加舒適。此外，車內還配備了 0 至 50°C 的冷熱一體式雪櫃，為乘客提供便利。</p><p><a title="_DSC2669" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238251/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238251_f34fe92051_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2669" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2674" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54074358072/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54074358072_424ac54b7b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2674" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2676" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075495483/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075495483_1069905386_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2676" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2680" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075562439/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075562439_bbd2212b98_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2680" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2684" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075562384/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075562384_bfa4896a1e_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2684" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2689" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075495493/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075495493_7d881e0dd2_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2689" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>X9 在科技配置上也不落後，這款車型搭載了 800V 高壓 SiC 碳化矽平台，充電效能提升一倍，20 分鐘內即可將電池從 10% 充至 80%，有效應對長途和短途的駕駛需求。續航方面，長續航版 X9 的最大續航距離可達 575 公里 (WLTP)，這對於應對日常使用和長途旅行都十分有利。</p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2700" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075689100/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075689100_f03e7bced9_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2700" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2422" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075495393/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075495393_f821fe68ff_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2422" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2425" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075495373/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075495373_b18ce7e3f9_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2425" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2426" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238136/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238136_55d794019b_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2426" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2431" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075562319/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075562319_4555d08f69_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2431" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2443" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54074357997/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54074357997_9caf36c887_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2443" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>在安全配置方面，X9 擁有全球量產最大 12,000 噸位壓鑄一體式車身，令整車剛度達到 46,000 Nm/deg，確保車身結構的穩定性和耐用性。此外，X9 還配備了 17 項主動安全功能，為駕駛者和乘客提供全面的保護，確保行車安全。同時，X9 亦具備大灣區聯保服務，令車主在珠三角地區行駛時更加安心。</p><p><a title="IMG_2445" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54074357967/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54074357967_c61161b315_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2445" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2457" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238071/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238071_9574254a43_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2457" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2466" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075689045/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075689045_c8c8c10e88_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2466" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2469" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075495313/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075495313_b24d752600_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2469" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2479" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238011/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238011_e3297466a1_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2479" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2484" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54074357902/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54074357902_3f0975b666_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2484" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2487" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075562254/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075562254_26704fca74_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2487" width="768" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2493" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238026/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238026_f63cf3ffbc_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2493" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td valign="middle"><b>型號</b></td><td valign="middle"><b>XPENG</b><b>小鵬汽車右軚版明日星艦</b><b>MPV X9</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" valign="middle"><b><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span></b></td></tr><tr><td valign="middle"><b>電池容量</b><b> (kWh)</b></td><td valign="middle">標準版 84.5</p><p>長續航版 101.5</td></tr><tr><td valign="middle"><b>最大續航距離</b><b> (km) (WLTP combine)</b></td><td valign="middle">標準版 480</p><p>長續航版 575</td></tr><tr><td valign="middle"><b>最大功率</b><b> (kW)</b></td><td valign="middle">235</td></tr><tr><td valign="middle"><b>最大